<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كُنَّا نُرَقِّعْهَا فَقَدْ مُزِّقَتْ ... واتَّسَعَ الخَرْقُ عَلَى الرَّاقِعِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فجزم نُرَقِّعُهَا،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَالَتْ سُلَيْمَى اشْتَرْ لَنَا دَقِيقَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَاشْتَرْ وَعَجِّلْ خَادِمًا لَبِيقَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">فجزم واشْتَرِ ومثله:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>لا تُؤَخِّرْ عَمَلَ اليَوْمِ لِغَدْ ... إِنَّ فِي غَدْكَ إِذَا جَاءَ عَمَلْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَإِذَا مَا العَمَلانِ اجْتَمَعَا ... عَمَلَا يَوْمَيْنِ فِي يَوْمٍ ثَقُلْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فجزم <span class="c1">"لِغَدٍ"</span> و<span class="c1">"فِي غَدِكَ"</span> ومثله:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَنْحَى عَلَيَّ الدَّهْرُ رِجْلًا وَيَدَا<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>يُقْسِمُ لَا يُصْلِحُ إِلَّا أَفْسَدَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَيُصْلِحُ اليَوْمَ وَيُفْسِدْهُ غَدَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">فجزم يُفْسِدُهُ ومثله:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>